title: That 70's Show Season 1
description:
This is the first season of That 70's Show. I watch this on my psp all the time with official firmware, but i dont know if it will work on ipod or zune.

There are 4 mp4 files, each around 500mb, they are the four discs ripped with magic dvd ripper on high settings. Each disc is 2 hours and 15 minutes long except for the first disc which is 2 hours and 38 minutes.

Please Seed This Great Show
